-- Risanamento approves sale of French assets to Chelsfiel/The Olayan Group-source
-- 
-- Fri Mar 14, 2014 04:52AM EDT
-- None



MILAN, March 14 (Reuters) - The board of Italian property company Risanamento <RN.MI> has given the final green light to the sale of prized Paris properties to Chelsfield/The Olayan Group, a source close to the matter said confirming a press report.

